you can define the VUs, Duration, Interations... via CLI: k6 run test-file.js -vus 1 -duration 10s -iterations 1

To bypass insecure requests, it's just run the command: k6 run test-file.js --insecure-skip-tls-verify

To output in JSON format you can run the command: k6 run script.js --summary-export=result.json


More CLI options you can check in the k6 documentation: https://k6.io/docs/using-k6/k6-options/how-to/